Build with:
docker build -t pal_graphite .


Run in background:
docker run -d -p 80:80 -p 3000:3000 pal_graphite


Run in interactive:
docker run -it -p 80:80 -p 3000:3000 pal_graphite bash


Persistent storage

Create volumens

docker volume create graphite

docker run -d -p 80:80 -p 3000:3000 -v graphite:/var/lib/graphite pal_graphite

